Introduction
============
Thanks for downloading HSL software. You can find out more information about
HSL by visiting our website: http://www.hsl.rl.ac.uk/

This package is intended to be used exclusively with IPOPT. To obtain the full
version of the packages please download them from the HSL web address above,
from which source code is also available.

Experimental!
=============
This binary distribution is still experimental. We would like to hear if you
have any problems so they can be rectified. Please send any feedback to
hsl@stfc.ac.uk

Installation 
============

Option 1: [To ensure Ipopt can find at compile time; or to run]
Copy the contents of lib/ into /usr/local/lib.
Copy the contents of include/ into /usr/local/include.
Run ldconfig.

Option 2: [To run with precompiled Ipopt]
Copy lib/libcoinhsl.so into your Ipopt directory and
ensure it is in your LD_LIBRARY_PATH.
